WEBVTT

00:03.437 --> 00:06.338
I may not be able to make it.

00:06.340 --> 00:07.406
Right.

00:07.408 --> 00:09.742
Mom, I know
it's your anniversary,

00:09.744 --> 00:12.177
but they may extend me
till October.

00:12.179 --> 00:15.647
Well, it's a war.
I don't control it.

00:15.649 --> 00:19.351
Right, I know. Mom... Okay.

00:19.353 --> 00:20.753
Right, listen, I got to go.

00:20.755 --> 00:22.588
My commander just came in.
We got casualties coming in.

00:22.590 --> 00:26.258
Right.
Love you. Yeah.

