person, don't you,

32:03.422 --> 32:05.589
for not wanting to speak to him?

32:05.591 --> 32:10.560
I think I have no right
to judge anybody on anything.

32:26.345 --> 32:28.679
Hey.

32:30.716 --> 32:34.184
Hey.

32:36.488 --> 32:38.322
How's Jorge?

32:38.324 --> 32:40.123
