and...

32:52.237 --> 32:53.704
Jordan, I know the hell
you went through

32:53.706 --> 32:55.205
with T.C.
When he first came back.

32:57.209 --> 32:58.442
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

33:00.212 --> 33:01.212
Forget it.

33:05.551 --> 33:08.318
This wasn't about me
coming back too soon.

33:08.320 --> 33:10.387
This case just brought up
some other stuff

33:10.389 --> 33:11.655
that I didn't want to admit to.

33:11.657 --> 33:14.224
Like what?

33:14.226 --> 33:16.460
I haven't told my parents
I'm back.

33:16.462 --> 33:18.996
It's their 40th anniversary.
I'm supposed to go.

33:20.699 --> 33:22.265
