used to be best friends.

33:39.785 --> 33:43.620
We watched games together,
went to games together,

33:43.622 --> 33:45.122
we played every sport.

33:45.124 --> 33:47.424
We did everything together.

33:51.096 --> 33:53.630
And then when I came out to him,

33:53.632 --> 33:57.334
it's like he couldn't talk
to me anymore.

33:57.336 --> 33:59.102
Honey, I'm so sorry.

34:00.506 --> 34:02.339
It's the same
Steelers game, right?

34:02.341 --> 34:04.141
I mean, what's the difference?

34:05.310 --> 34:06.550
But to him, it had all changed.

34:08.795 --> 34:11.112
So I figure
if I don't say anything,

34:11.116 --> 34:17.788
maybe for a year or two...
You know,

34:17.790 --> 34:20.456
maybe there's
that glimmer of hope.

34:20.458 --> 34:22.826
Even if it's just 1% that...

34:25.330 --> 34:26.530
he'll change and then things

34:26.532 --> 34:28.431
